{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to version 1.14 of the library the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the type’s isolation."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"That now changes in 1.14 where ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","type":"reference"},{"text":" is now officially ","type":"text"},{"code":"@MainActor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"-isolated. This has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","te